            <div type="content">
                <div type="intro">
                <p>In this index is displayed the set of rules designed for SigiDoc in order to 
                    extract (potentially) all the information coming from a seal's legend and 
                    organise it in indices automatically generated through EFES. The following thematic list 
                    contains the most relevant topics, unavoidable in sigillographic indices and traditionally appearing in most of the 
                    sigillographic corpora: however, the ultimate choice about the themes represented in indices belongs to each projet, expanding or shortening this list, 
                    but, especially in the latter case, it is strongly recommended to keep a common range of indices among the projects using SigiDoc, in order to ensure interoperability and searchability.</p>
                <p>This represents the first step in creating and populating indices: for complete 
                    guidance, please, follow the <ref target="https://github.com/EpiDoc/EFES/wiki/Indices">EFES guidelines</ref>.</p>
            </div>
